INSERT INTO "news" VALUES(1,1,'Archive now fully populated',replace('Hey, just lettin'' everyone know that the site was temporarily down while I populated the database with the old write-offs. That''s rightâ€”[the archive](http://writeoff.rogerdodger.me/archive) now contains every bit of write-off history!\n\n**Important!**\nRemember that artist names are reserved to the first people who get them. The way this works is by taking the set of all artists and subtracting any attached to your user account from the set. This set contains a list of artist names that you may not submit as. Now, because the old data contains names from people who aren''t registered, or names that don''t quite associate with any user account, a lot of names are going to be "stuck in limbo" and unusable.\n\nThe [My Submissions](http://writeoff.rogerdodger.me/user/me) page should contain all of your submissions. If any of your stories happen to not be in that list, [let me know](http://writeoff.rogerdodger.me/contact). I''ve tried to associate the old stories with user accounts as best as possible, but there''s a lot of them (and I''m tired).\n','\n',char(10)),'2012-11-14 16:50:00','2012-11-14 16:50:00');
INSERT INTO "news" VALUES(2,1,'DDoS downtime',replace('MLPchan''s servers experienced a DDoS over the last couple hours, which is why the site was unavailable. And the Hearth''s Warming Care Package deadline is right about now. Because of work or other commitments, I understand that the last few hours may have been the only time some people may have had to submit today. As such, the deadline''s been extended by 24 hours to make sure nobody missed out because of this issue.\n\nSorry for the inconvenience.\n','\n',char(10)),'2012-11-17 17:45:00','2012-11-17 17:45:00');
INSERT INTO "news" VALUES(3,1,'A wild sidebar appears',replace(replace('It''s been bugging me for a while now how poor the event navigation is, so here''s a pretty little sidebar to solve that. It comes with news too, because having news hidden away in a tab that nobody looks at is a worse idea than chopping carrots with a wet noodle.\r\n\r\nSo if you''re one of the lucky ones whose horizontal resolution is more than 1150 pixels, welcome to the cool kids club. If not, how''d you get here anyway?','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),'2013-02-15 20:09:01','2013-02-15 20:10:16');
INSERT INTO "news" VALUES(4,1,'Server move',replace(replace('Some of you may have noticed the site was in read-only mode for a while. MLPchan moved server again, so I had to make the site read only while I was installing the hundreds of modules this application depends on for the hundredth time.\r\n\r\nAnyway, should be all good now. Let me know if you encounter any problems.','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),'2013-02-18 02:22:04','2013-02-18 02:22:04');
INSERT INTO "news" VALUES(5,1,'Whoa, some changes!',replace(replace('You see the new title? It''s got like pretty Unicode symbols instead of just dashes now! Pretty neat, right?\r\n\r\nOn a more serious note, I''ve now got some scripts for merging artists/users, meaning those of you who foolishly used different-but-similar names for your submissions can now have those all put under one name. Just let me know if you want this done.','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),'2013-06-23 15:03:31','2013-06-23 15:03:53');
